Defense Implementation:
Adversarial training was used as the defense technique. 
The model was retrained using adversarial examples generated by FGSM. 
This helped the model learn from manipulated inputs and improved its ability to resist attacks. 
After defense training, the model accuracy under attack increased significantly to 97.66%.

Code:
